<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color:#6BAB30;"><span style="font-size:70%;"><strong>Graciously donated by a Richard Michael Maisnon (possibly an alias) on behalf of the Center for Eschatological and Trascendental Research. CETRes officials later contacted the Health and Prevention Mission Director (Dr. Lucía Robres) to deliver detailed indications on how to operate the asset.</strong></span></span></p>
</div>
<p><span style="font-size:130%;"><span style="color:#6BAB30;"><strong>Of Interest:</strong></span></span> <em>user-friendly, sessile (to water), non-hazardous organism, designed organism (Animalia, Mammalia?, Artiodactyla? - unclassed), abnormal entropy, ongoing research, ongoing programme, sentience?, intelligence?, donation?, prospective Specialist member?</em></p>
<span style="font-size:130%;"><span style="color:#6BAB30;"><strong>Asset Summary:</strong></span></span> <em>Transcript of the vocal report performed by Dr. Lucía Robres, Health and Prevention Director, to her MCF co-workers.</em><br />
<script type="text/javascript" src="http://d3g0gp89917ko0.cloudfront.net/v--3e3a6f7dbcc9/common--javascript/yahooui/tabview-min.js">
</script>
<div id="wiki-tabview-8c428f0f8f593a12959b2bed02cb62ba" class="yui-navset">
<ul class="yui-nav">
<li class="selected"><a href="javascript:;"><em>MWB Newsletter Report 03 - 1-CETR-D</em></a></li>
