<div style="text-align: justify;">
<p><em>The conclusions of the report involving the First CETRes donation, informally known as &quot;the Hippo&quot;, as written by Mr. Lin Jong, Health and Prevention Research Executive member, follows.</em></p>
<script type="text/javascript" src="http://d3g0gp89917ko0.cloudfront.net/v--3e3a6f7dbcc9/common--javascript/yahooui/tabview-min.js">
</script>
<div id="wiki-tabview-0775673d0621f06e4f45a761f5260b9d" class="yui-navset">
<ul class="yui-nav">
<li class="selected"><a href="javascript:;"><em>MWB Newsletter Report 05 - 1-CETR-D</em></a></li>
